p>DHL 宣布其 FAST-TRACK Sessions 人才搜寻将于 2024 年回归。</p><p>该机会向全球所有艺术家和乐队开放，并寻求通过提供专业录音经验和音乐行业专家的机会来支持新兴人才。</p><p>三名获奖者将在伦敦传奇的 Abbey Road Studios 获得录制时间，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">披头士乐队</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/amy-winehouse">艾米·怀恩豪斯</a>以及弗兰克·奥恩等现代偶像此前曾在这里录制过音乐。在为期三天的录制过程中，录音室专家和工程师将与 Hannah V 一起参与录制，Hannah V 是一位金牌唱片制作人和词曲作者，曾与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stormzy">Stormzy</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yola">Yola</a>等人合作过。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C5S67BarX0G/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,3